          "content": "_aj_: what about: {past_avg += 1} on every insertion into the queue, and on every send {to_send = min(queue, max(TARGET_RATE, past_avg * (1 - Q))); past_avg = (past_avg - to_send) * Q}, where Q = exp(-TIMEOUT/AVG_SEND_INTERVAL)",
